{"tid":324708,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"欣宜教大家食野點樣唔囤積脂肪","createTime":"2017-07-16T15:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T02:38:21.000Z","uid":102421,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"299975fcb3249ab2be053934c186d0fa23145117","tid":324708,"uid":102421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"台灣癌症基金會<strong>營養師鄭欣宜</strong>答：運動後肌肉修補需大量低脂蛋白質食物和適量碳水化合物作為能量來源，想加強肌肉線條的民眾，建議攝取茶葉蛋、雞胸肉、魚肉或豆漿等優質蛋白質食物，以促進肌肉生長，且最好別吃豬肉、牛肉等紅肉，因紅肉脂肪含量較高，吃下肚易囤積脂肪，強化肌肉線條的效果較差。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170715/1159634/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170715%2F1159634%2F&d=pbD15bkCEPrEdFYL%2Fljb4%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=0ddd9246\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170715/1159634/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/233455_4abf2babb1ec4d109aa7873b36e631ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F233455_4abf2babb1ec4d109aa7873b36e631ac.jpg&h=f22e0879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n營養師欣宜小時候不注重營養, 故長大後攻讀營養學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/233556_d31864eca5d6db4f66c8eaaeb3585245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F233556_d31864eca5d6db4f66c8eaaeb3585245.jpg&h=a8950ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n營養師欣宜示範均衡飲食。"},{"pid":"7f74704500ea36f57de3f7490054f99f7791f2ed","tid":324708,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"得把聲J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbd606c3a96d7d684361db623d9b3004ba8f0b1","tid":324708,"uid":115972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"欣宜教大家點樣唔食野囤積脂肪"},{"pid":"3b44181692c73a51f